Task5: Use dopcker provider with terraform to launch  nginx container.

1. install docker (sudo apt install docker.io )
2. enable docker run permissions to ubuntu user
      chown ubuntu:ubuntu /var/run/docker.sock
3. copy docker main.tf file
4. run terraform commands.

